('Cannot find module with alias in production build - alias not resolving in parcel build', 'bundler', 'MEDIUM', '[{"solution": "Use glob alias syntax in package.json: {\"alias\": {\"actions/*\": \"./client/actions/$1\"}}", "percentage": 89}, {"solution": "Ensure alias path is relative from package.json location, not entry point", "percentage": 83}]'::jsonb, 'Parcel v1 or v2, package.json with alias field', 'Aliased imports resolve in both dev and production builds', 'Using simple alias in v2 (requires glob pattern), path relative to entry file instead of package root', 0.86, 'haiku', NOW(), 'https://stackoverflow.com/questions/54052884', 'admin:1764227081');
